cs.LG, cs.AR, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.SY

This paper proposes a method for training deep neural networks that reduces computational complexity, making it suitable for edge devices. The paper focuses on the implementation of the training procedure in the log-domain with fixed-point data representations, which is a topic that falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of this method for image classification tasks (cs.CV) and the potential for hardware implementation (cs.AR, cs.SY). Finally, the paper also discusses the use of approximations in the log-domain, which is a topic that falls under the category of numerical analysis (cs.NE).
